Kien: Have you found a job yet Minh?

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:24.000
Minh: I haven't, do you have a job I can work with?

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Kien: My job is just writing reports and making posters for social media.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Kien: If you work with me, it will take months for you to pay off your debt.